{"prompt": "Design a portfolio for a scientific researcher. The site should be clear, featuring a clean, bright yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Dr. Evelyn Reed - Scientific Researcher</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #fdfd96; /* Bright yellow */\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: #ffd700; /* Slightly darker yellow for header */\n            color: #333;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #e6c300 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        #main {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n        #main h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #ccad00;\n        }\n        .section {\n            background: #fff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .section h3 {\n            color: #e6c300;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #fdfd96;\n            padding-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n        .publication-list {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n        }\n        .publication-list li {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            padding-left: 20px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        .publication-list li::before {\n            content: \"\\2022\";\n            color: #ffd700;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 1em;\n            margin-left: -1em;\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 0;\n        }\n        .publication-list a {\n            color: #007bff;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        .publication-list a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            color: #fff;\n            background-color: #ffd700;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 95%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            header p {\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Dr. Evelyn Reed</h1>\n            <p>Passionate Scientific Researcher in Molecular Biology</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n            <h3>About Me</h3>\n            <p>Dr. Evelyn Reed is a dedicated researcher with a focus on understanding the intricate mechanisms of cellular communication. Her work aims to uncover novel therapeutic targets for a range of diseases, utilizing cutting-edge techniques in molecular biology and genomics.</p>\n            <p>With over 10 years of experience in academic research, Dr. Reed has contributed significantly to the field through rigorous experimentation and insightful analysis.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"research-interests\" class=\"section\">\n            <h3>Research Interests</h3>\n            <ul>\n                <li>Signal Transduction Pathways</li>\n                <li>Gene Regulation</li>\n                <li>Cellular Aging</li>\n                <li>Drug Discovery</li>\n                <li>Genomic Instability</li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"publications\" class=\"section\">\n            <h3>Selected Publications</h3>\n            <ul class=\"publication-list\">\n                <li>Reed, E., et al. (2023). \"Unraveling the role of Protein X in cellular senescence.\" *Journal of Cellular Biology*, 15(2), 112-125. <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">[Link]</a></li>\n                <li>Smith, J., Reed, E., et al. (2022). \"Novel inhibitors targeting Pathway Y for cancer therapy.\" *Nature Medicine*, 28(5), 870-885. <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">[Link]</a></li>\n                <li>Reed, E., Lee, K. (2021). \"Epigenetic modifications in age-related neurodegeneration.\" *Trends in Molecular Science*, 35(8), 650-665. <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">[Link]</a></li>\n                <li>Davis, R., Reed, E. (2020). \"CRISPR-based screening identifies new regulators of DNA repair.\" *Cell Reports*, 30(1), 15-28. <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">[Link]</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n            <h3>Contact</h3>\n            <p>Email: evelyn.reed@example.com</p>\n            <p>LinkedIn: <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">linkedin.com/in/evelynreed</a></p>\n            <p>ResearchGate: <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">researchgate.net/profile/Evelyn_Reed</a></p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2024 Dr. Evelyn Reed. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}